profile:
Work that we do include:
- Painting, residential and commercial.

- Sound proofing and mitigation, residential and commercial; sound insulation wall panels.

- Draft-proofing and winterizing to minimize heat and energy loss, which will reduce energy costs and increase comfort.

- Installing faux thin-brick wall covering.

- Handyman projects around the home, including light fixture install, hanging doors, wall repairs.

- Vinyl lettering, signage and photo panel installation.

- Re-caulking and grout repair in shower stalls and tub surrounds.

- Art preparation and installation.

- Pre-Realty Listing home enhancements.

- Drywall installation and repair.

- Parging

- Ikea product hacking/modification, assembly and install. 

- Custom built-ins and shelf units.
